{"pv29:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv29:0.2":"Culavagga ","pv29:0.3":"4. Bhusapetavatthu ","pv29:1.1":"“Bhusani eko salim punaparo, ","pv29:1.2":"Ayanca nari sakamamsalohitam; ","pv29:1.3":"Tuvanca gutham asucim akantam, ","pv29:1.4":"Paribhunjasi kissa ayam vipako”ti. ","pv29:2.1":"“Ayam pure mataram himsati, ","pv29:2.2":"Ayam pana kutavanijo; ","pv29:2.3":"Ayam mamsani khaditva, ","pv29:2.4":"Musavadena vanceti. ","pv29:3.1":"Aham manussesu manussabhuta, ","pv29:3.2":"Agarini sabbakulassa issara; ","pv29:3.3":"Santesu pariguhami, ","pv29:3.4":"Ma ca kinci ito adam. ","pv29:4.1":"Musavadena chademi, ","pv29:4.2":"‘natthi etam mama gehe; ","pv29:4.3":"Sace santam niguhami, ","pv29:4.4":"gutho me hotu bhojanam’. ","pv29:5.1":"Tassa kammassa vipakena, ","pv29:5.2":"musavadassa cubhayam; ","pv29:5.3":"Sugandham salino bhattam, ","pv29:5.4":"gutham me parivattati. ","pv29:6.1":"Avanjhani ca kammani, ","pv29:6.2":"Na hi kammam vinassati; ","pv29:6.3":"Duggandham kiminam milam, ","pv29:6.4":"Bhunjami ca pivami ca”ti. ","pv29:7.1":"Bhusapetavatthu catuttham. "}